{"TopicId":132736,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Has anyone else drawn parallels between Kerbals and Minions?","CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-22T22:25:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-22T22:25:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow before people come in and saying that they hate the Minions to death, I just wanna have a discussion on their similarities.\u00A0For those who don\u0027t know, I suppose this thread won\u0027t make a whole lot of sense, but the Minions are little yellow creatures from the Despicable Me series of animated movies.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEver since I\u0027ve both seen the movies and played KSP, it\u0027s interesting to see how similar the two little things really are. Both very small, both cutesy, both having low intelligence but somehow having the skills to build rockets, and a seemingly endless supply of \u003Cem\u003Enearly\u003C/em\u003E identical individuals. Add that, plus the made-up languages they both use, and their premise seems incredibly similar apart from the Minion\u0027s genetic need to be enslaved to a powerful being.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anyone else ever noted anything like this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-22T22:30:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve definitely noticed the similarities.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-22T22:51:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs I explained to my daughter - some of the minions left their home planet of Kerbin, got lost in space, and landed on Earth. And as we now know from Minion history (The Minion Movie), they\u0027ve been here ever since, always lending a hand when we can\u0027t get things quite right...\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T00:24:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI definitely think of my Kerbals as Minions... but what does that make me???\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T00:31:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222425051\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456187086\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI definitely think of my Kerbals as Minions... but what does that make me???\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell the \u00A0\u0022I\u0027m not out to conquer the galaxy.... I swear...\u0022 looks as reliable as\u00A0\u0022democratic people republic\u0022 in the first place\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nDownloading all the BDarmory mods.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frybert","CreatedById":97766,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T00:31:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T00:33:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022f