squote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah...... you may not want to read my fan-fiction piece then.... lol.... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt makes you - Gru! Gru of Kerbin! (insert evil laugh here)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GeneralVeers","CreatedById":148918,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T01:48:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhaaaaaat??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals are \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,128,0);\u0022\u003EGREEN.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinions are \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(255,215,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYELLOW.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is just no similarity here. At. All.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T01:54:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222425170\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456192100\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148918\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GeneralVeers\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, GeneralVeers said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhaaaaaat??\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals are \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,128,0);\u0022\u003EGREEN.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinions are \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(255,215,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EYELLOW.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is just no similarity here. At. All.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlants are green (And Kerbals are green) And Minions are yellow (And the sun is Yellow), and without the Sun, plants die, Wait... where was I going with this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-23T04:14:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222425178\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456192472\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152800\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceception\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Spaceception said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlants are green (And Kerbals are green) And Minions are yellow (And the sun is Yellow), and without the Sun, plants die, Wait... where was I going with this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe sun is yellow, and it works because of fusion. Minions are yellow, therefore they work because of fusion. Plants need fusion to survive, because the Sun makes light with fusion. Therefore, plants need minions to survive. Kerbals are green, therefore they are plants, therefore Kerbals need minions to survive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GeneralVeers","CreatedById":148918,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-24T22:04:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222425178\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022132736\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456192472\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152800\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceception\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 2/23/2016 at 6:54 PM, Spaceception said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlants are green (And Kerbals are green) And Minions are yellow (And the sun is Yellow), and without the Sun, plants die, Wait... where was I going with this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBakersfield. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022^_^\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022^_^\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlants are, as you say, \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Egreen.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E Minions are, as you say, \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFD700;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Eyellow.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E Therefore there is no similarity between plants and minions. See? That works out fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T03:10:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKerbals are not stupid. They\u0027re just over-eager. That said, there\u0027s definitely some similarities, but not enough to make me suggest that one stole from the other. The Little Green (or yellow I guess) Man is a trope that dates back to the 50s.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T05:23:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs only one Kerbal can be active at once - the one, possessed by its Master (the player), then...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso there are immortal Chosen: Val, Jeb, Bob, Bill.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThey wear orange robes, rather than usual white robes: as a sigil of their spiritual force, rather than others\u0027 innocence...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-25T05:26:41Z\u0022 title=\u002202/25/2016 05:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 25, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GeneralVeers","CreatedById":148918,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-25T07:35:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUhhh.....\u0022\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(255,140,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EORANGE\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E shirts\u0022???\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s a little too close to \u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(255,0,0);\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERED\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E shirts.......\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}